law.history: Repealed 2008 Ky. Acts ch. 155, sec. 1, effective July 15, 2008. -- Created 2006 Ky. Acts ch. 164, sec. 2, effective July 12, 2006.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Comprehensive dental and vision insurance and health discount plans for state employees on voluntary payroll deduction basis -- Administrative regulations.
